Title: Magnesium Atomic Potential
Mg_a_out                 output file name. If blank, data will show on screen
  12.00000               zed: atomic number
   0.00000               moment
    1                    number of spins
    1                    ex-cor type (1=vb-hedin,2=vosko)
   25                    number of iterations
   0.20000               mixing parameter
Mg_a_pot                 pot file (output)
